>> source: https://recipe.awesomedrinks.com/recipe/clover-club/

Add @gin{45%ml}, @fresh lime juice{22.5%ml}, @simple syrup{22.5%ml}, @raspberries{5} into a #cocktail shaker{} with ice and shake for ~{10%seconds}.

Then, discard the ice, add @egg white{15%ml} and shake again for ~{15%seconds}. -- this is know as "dry shake"

Strain into a chilled #coupe glass{}, garnish with @raspberries{3} on a spear.
